[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "mqtt-rs"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "mqtt-rs"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
ctrlc = "3.4.4"
dotenv = "0.15.0"
json = "0.12.4"
rand = "0.8.5"
rumqttc = "0.24.0"
serde_json = "1.0.120"

[dependencies.redis]
version = "0.25.3"
features = ["tokio-comp"]

[dependencies.rocket]
version = "0.5.1"
features = ["json", "serde_json"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.204"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.38.1"
features = ["full"]
